{"tid":1848624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係痴撚線，剛大陸返來，唔吊唔得","createTime":"2020-01-28T14:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T15:02:43.000Z","uid":341589,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1ebe50d45ab91af5c0605015df65bbf2ca098b","tid":1848624,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"今日有急事要返大陸走一轉。一早過皇崗，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><em>過大陸關要填申報表入境，</em></span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港唔使</span></span>。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">心諗正常啊！出境唔理您，所以香港唔使填。</span></strong></span><br />\n下午同屋企人返來，一行四人，照舊係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><em>大陸關填申報表出境，心諗都正常啊，如果您填常住地係湖北/武漢可能會詳細檢查下。</em></span></strong></span>點知去到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港關</span></span></span>，我同屋企人都可以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>直行直過</strong></span></span></span>，中間無填過任何資料，關員亦都無問我地從邊度返來？於時專登過關後，立刻回頭望，原來所有人都係直行直過，包括強國人。去度呢度，心諗：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><em><strong><ins>「無撚嘢呀，屌！您9問一句都無？咁真係自出自入，冇掩雞籠，痴撚線」</ins></strong></em></span></span><br />\n另外在皇巴上觀察，雖然人流少左，但超過一半都係內地同胞。<br />\n<br />\n如果有<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手足做海關/入境，可否澄清一下？</span></span></em></strong> 我 check返係機場同高鐵站先要填表，但真係唔需要問嗎？"},{"pid":"6e65fad214d8de607a88e2789fda7e55cb3966bf","tid":1848624,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:37:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"986699edf023a3ce2baca70377dd607e17122dc9","tid":1848624,"uid":341589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ex68DOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEx68DOY.jpg&h=c5fd38f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">其實今日親眼見，每個入市嘅收費站，每個人都要探熱檢查。如果有發燒，就唔俾入市。有地方甚至講明外地人唔俾入，香港仲大開中門。</span>"}]}